flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B[Receive Request]
    B --> C{Authenticated?}

    C -- No --> C1[Redirect to Login]
    C1 --> C2{Login success?}
    C2 -- No --> X[End - Auth Failed]
    C2 -- Yes --> D[Create Session]

    C -- Yes --> D[Load Session]

    D --> E[Preprocess Input]
    E --> F{Valid Input?}

    F -- No --> F1[Return Validation Error]
    F1 --> X

    F -- Yes --> G{Check Cache}

    G -- Hit --> G1[Return Cached Response]
    G1 --> X

    G -- Miss --> H[Intent Detection]

    H --> I{Intent Recognized?}

    I -- No --> I1[Fallback Response]
    I1 --> I2{Fallback Count > 2?}

    I2 -- Yes --> I3[Escalate to Human]
    I3 --> X

    I2 -- No --> I4[Suggest Options]
    I4 --> B

    I -- Yes --> J{Intent Type}

    J -- FAQ --> J1[Fetch from Knowledge Base]
    J1 --> J2[Store in Cache]
    J2 --> X

    J -- Transaction --> K[Validate Entities]
    K --> K1{Entities valid?}

    K1 -- No --> K2[Ask for Missing Data]
    K2 --> B

    K1 -- Yes --> L[Call Backend API]
    L --> L1{Timeout?}

    L1 -- Yes --> L2[Retry API x2]
    L2 --> L3{Still failing?}

    L3 -- Yes --> L4[Send to Async Queue]
    L4 --> L5[Notify User: Processing]
    L5 --> X

    L3 -- No --> L6[Process Response]
    L6 --> L7[Store in Cache]
    L7 --> X

    L1 -- No --> L8{Success?}

    L8 -- No --> L9[Return Error]
    L9 --> X

    L8 -- Yes --> L6

    J -- Generative --> M[Send Prompt to LLM]
    M --> M1{LLM Error?}

    M1 -- Yes --> M2[Fallback Response]
    M2 --> X

    M1 -- No --> M3[Post-process Output]
    M3 --> M4{Safe Output?}

    M4 -- No --> M5[Apply Safety Filter]
    M5 --> X

    M4 -- Yes --> X

    J -- Sensitive --> N[Apply Policy]
    N --> X

    J -- Escalation --> O[Transfer to Agent]
    O --> X

    X[End]